FBIS4-68205 "jptot021__l94009" JPRS-TOT-94-021-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 16 May 1994 LATIN AMERICA ARGENTINA ORP Denies Attack on Japanese Embassy ORP Denies Attack on Japanese Embassy PY1605183094 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS in Spanish 0010 GMT 16 May 94 PY1605183094 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS Spanish BFN [Excerpt] Buenos Aires, 15 May (NA) -- The People's Revolutionary Army (ORP) today denied any involvement in the attack on the Japanese Embassy on 13 May and blamed incriminating reports on "counterintelligence maneuvers." [see item PY1305161194 in previous Terrorism Report] The ORP states that pamphlets linking the ORP to the attack "are a pathetic attempt to involve the organization in an incident that is without political motive." The ORP press communique stresses that it has "always" admitted responsibility for its actions, adding that this "attempt" to link it to the attack "a pathetic counterintelligence maneuver." [passage omitted]
